<p style="text-indent: 2em;">JDWhale Smart Screen i8 Pro has an 8-inch oversized smart screen providing HD image quality, with a resolution of up to 1280*800. It is compact and thin, with a waistline more ergonomic and aesthetic, providing better hand-touch feeling. Meanwhile, the product supports 12-hour ultra-long standby time. Two 2,500mAh extra-large capacity batteries make the product always within touch everywhere at home and free from the power line.</p>
<p><br/></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;">JDWhale Smart Screen i8 Pro is equipped with the far-field voice interaction supported by 4 microphone arrays, supports customized awakening and other futuristic technologies, presents voice interaction within 5m in an indoor environment and accurate voice recognition; with Wi-Fi 2.4G+5G dual-frequency mode, it can guarantee the Wi-Fi network speed and through-wall ability, provide the best visual comfort and audiovisual experience without video lag for users; two 5W loudspeakers constitute the 2.0 sound track, and the bass passive enhancement unit improves the acoustic quality, allowing users to enjoy the effects of desktop home theater; 5 mega-pixel camera provides HD video chat, and better privacy protection with a physical shelter switch.</p>
