<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;">As a technology and service enterprise based on the supply chain, JD Group relies on its own scenario to develop and improve AI, cloud computing, IoT and other technologies in more than 10 industries including retail, logistics, finance, insurance, real estate and health. As the representative for the technology and service system in one of the four core business domains of JD, JD Cloud & AI has just completed the brand upgrading, integrated cloud, AI, IoT, big data and other cutting-edge technologies and capabilities, connected the physical and digital world, and become a driver for digital, network and intelligent upgrading.</p>
<p><br/></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;">In the process of vigorous promotion of “new infrastructure construction” in China, interconnection will be further enhanced not only between humans but also between human and object and between objects, which will make connection among entities in the physical world stronger. After the brand upgrading of JD Cloud & AI, the system capabilities among cloud, AI, IoT and other technologies are connected to provide richer contents and application scenarios for users. With the reachability to consumers and service ability to users, JD Cloud & AI enables users to enjoy good products, favorable prices, good services and excellent experience, including personalized products and services, more conveniently.</p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;">The smart loudspeaker box launched this time also has the personalized service ability as JD accumulated from years of efforts. JDWhale Smart Screen i8 Pro is equipped with “one-sentence” JD shopping function, users can experience voice+touch screen dual-mode shopping experience via the loudspeaker box, and directly query the commodities with promotions. Users buying the loudspeaker box can enjoy coupons for new users, which will be provided to users directly. As the family control center, the loudspeaker box frees users’ hands, controls other JDWhale devices by voice control, implements cooperation among various scenarios, and realizes control of home appliances, such as air conditioners, purifiers, humidifiers, bulbs and sockets, with “one sentence”. At the same time, encyclopedia Q&A will also be provided with “one sentence”. Recipe query, weather query, alarm clock setting, reminder setting, traffic control query, news listening and other functions will also be provided for convenience in life, saving users’ time, improving life quality, and bringing good experience.</p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><strong>Connect Ecosystem  Create Future</strong></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p>
