<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;">There can be no doubt that the arrival of 5G era and further integration of cloud, AI and IoT will accelerate the closed loop reconstruction of new intelligent application scenarios, new cloud edge intelligent computing product forms and new data types, and make IoT closer.</p>
